text: Zygaspis maraisi is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Mozambique. ==References== Category:Zygaspis Category:Reptiles of Mozambique Category:Endemic fauna of Mozambique Category:Reptiles described in 2016 Category:Taxa named by Donald George Broadley Category:Taxa named by G.
